name: Uptime Dashboard Web App UI Kit
description:
Uptime Dashboard Web App UI Kit

Uptime Dashboard is a modern and professional Web App UI Kit to help you create a dashboard for your needs easily. It comes with neatly organized layers, 10+ components, and more than 10+ icons. The UI KIT is ready to use for your next project. Everything is perfectly organized and easy to modify, so you can customize it in a few minutes. This dashboard is a tool for managers, directors, and executives to organize, plan, monitor, and manage any project. The UI Kit includes 8 categories of elements that are ideal for desktop applications. All the components are carefully created and combined into 10+. So download and enjoy.
